@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

     Welcome to @{b}@{fg shine}@{bg fill}BeatBox 2@{ub}@{bg back} @{fg text}!

     This is an easy-to-use music program,allowing four
     tracks of samples to be used and everything controlled
     using buttons and menus (no nasty hex numbers here!).

     Note that it's never going to even approach OctaMED or
     Bars and Pipes for functionality (!) - it's mostly for
     people who want to make music and can't figure out/can't
     be bothered with complicated trackers :)
     
          
     @{"Features" link "Features" 0}

     This section tells you what BeatBox 2 can do.

     @{"GettingáStarted" link "Start" 0}

     This is a short introduction to beginning writing your
     own music with BeatBox 2.

     @{"Comments,questions,etc" link "Comments" 0}

     Tell us what you think,after reading this!

     @{"History" link "History" 0}

     How it all started.
@endnode

